DE MAIL END-->. I usually check my email daily, so barring unusual circumstances, I should respond within a day or two.<br><br>As Jaikar says, carry on.  <p><html><body><p style="font-size:110%"><b><a href="http://www.suckbird.com/roster/profile.asp?who=Iskandar" STYLE="text-decoration: none"  target="_blank">Veteran Iskandar Alazeem</a><br><a href=http://www.steelwarrior.org STYLE="text-decoration: none" target="_blank">Steel Warrior</a> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior STYLE="text-decoration: none"  target="_blank">moderator</a><br><a href=http://www.keepersofthefaith.org STYLE="text-decoration: none"  target="_blank">Keepers of the Faith</a></b></p></body></html></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showPrevMessage?topicID=682.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showNextMessage?topicID=682.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.emailToFriend?topicID=682.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.threadControl?topicID=682.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=682.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=682.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notific